INSTALL
=======


- get and install the plugins branch of chregu's fork of Phonegap at http://github.com/chregu/phonegap-iphone with
    
    git clone -b plugins git://github.com/chregu/phonegap-iphone.git
    cd phonegap-iphone
    make
    open  PhoneGapLibInstaller.pkg

- Make sure PHONEGAPLIB points to this (Preferences ... -> Source Trees)
- try to compile this project
- open the radioapp xcode project
- change the target to "radioapp-iPad"
- build & run


